      "abstract": "In the current issue of JAHA , Dalen et al[1][1] report the results of a single‐center prospective observational study of 47 patients with implantation of the Perceval sutureless bioprosthesis (LivaNova, Milan, Italy). Cardiac computed tomography (CT) performed at a median of 491 days (range 36"
